article.description: — Kino Lilly Jr. scored 22 points as Brown beat Rhode Island 67-64 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Lilly scores 22 in Brown's 67-64 victory against Rhode Island
article.linkText: Lilly scores 22 in Brown's 67-64 victory against Rhode Island
article.story: KINGSTON, R.I. -- — Kino Lilly Jr. scored 22 points as Brown beat Rhode Island 67-64 on Wednesday night. Lilly shot 6 for 15 (3 for 7 from 3-point range) and 7 of 10 from the free throw line for the Bears (3-8, Ivy League). Aaron Cooley shot 5 for 11, including 3 for 7 from beyond the arc to add 13 points. Kalu Anya went 5 of 7 from the field to finish with 11 points. Jaden House led the way for the Rams (5-4) with 16 points, four assists and two steals. David Fuchs added 11 points and eight rebounds for Rhode Island. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
